      "text": "四龙套、四大铠、吴桢、朱元璋同上。〖吹打〗。众人同下。",
      "text_length": 27
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023007_e00008",
      "play_id": "01023007",
      "scene_id": "01023007_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "四龙套、四番将同出城，刘福通上，看，坐。四龙套、四大铠、吴桢、朱元璋同上。",
      "text_length": 37
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023007_e00009",
      "play_id": "01023007",
      "scene_id": "01023007_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘福通"
      ],
      "text": "御弟！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023007_e00010",
      "play_id": "01023007",
      "scene_id": "01023007_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "朱元璋"
      ],
      "text": "皇兄！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023007_e00011",
      "play_id": "01023007",
      "scene_id": "01023007_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘福通"
      ],
      "text": "御弟请。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023007_e00012",
      "play_id": "01023007",
      "scene_id": "01023007_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "朱元璋"
      ],
      "text": "还是皇兄请。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023007_e00013",
      "play_id": "01023007",
      "scene_id": "01023007_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘福通"
      ],
      "text": "你我挽手而行。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023007_e00014",
      "play_id": "01023007",
      "scene_id": "01023007_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "众人同入城，同下。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023007_e00015",
      "play_id": "01023007",
      "scene_id": "01023007_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "蒋忠上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023007_e00016",
      "play_id": "01023007",
      "scene_id": "01023007_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "蒋忠"
      ],
      "text": "进得城来，不知我主哪里去了？看那厢老将军来也。",
      "text_length": 23
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023007_e00017",
      "play_id": "01023007",
      "scene_id": "01023007_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "吴桢上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023007_e00018",
      "play_id": "01023007",
      "scene_id": "01023007_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "吴桢"
      ],
      "text": "将军在此做甚？",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023007_e00019",
      "play_id": "01023007",
      "scene_id": "01023007_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "蒋忠"
      ],
      "text": "俺欲将战马拴在柳林，随同老将军前去保驾。",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023007_e00020",
      "play_id": "01023007",
      "scene_id": "01023007_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "吴桢"
      ],
      "text": "将军此言差矣！",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023007_e00021",
      "play_id": "01023007",
      "scene_id": "01023007_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "吴桢"
      ],
      "text": "大将军说话欠思量，大将无坐骑怎赴战场？望将军牵战马高坡上，有老夫保圣驾料也无妨。",
      "text_length": 40
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023007_e00022",
      "play_id": "01023007",
      "scene_id": "01023007_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "吴桢下。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023007_e00023",
      "play_id": "01023007",
      "scene_id": "01023007_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "蒋忠"
      ],
      "text": "老将军秉忠心把国掌，威风凛凛气刚强。我这里且把山坡上，准备战马再做主张。",
      "text_length": 36
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023007_e00024",
      "play_id": "01023007",
      "scene_id": "01023007_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "蒋忠下。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023007_e00025",
      "play_id": "01023007",
      "scene_id": "01023007_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "四龙套、四番将、四大铠、吴桢同上，刘福通扯朱元璋同上。",
      "text_length": 27
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023007_e00026",
      "play_id": "01023007",
      "scene_id": "01023007_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘福通"
      ],
      "text": "御弟驾到，孤家未曾远迎，面前恕罪。",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023007_e00027",
      "play_id": "01023007",
      "scene_id": "01023007_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "朱元璋"
      ],
      "text": "岂敢，小弟来得卤莽，皇兄海涵。",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023007_e00028",
      "play_id": "01023007",
      "scene_id": "01023007_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘福通"
      ],
      "text": "岂敢。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023007_e00029",
      "play_id": "01023007",
      "scene_id": "01023007_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "朱元璋"
      ],
      "text": "皇兄见召，必有所为。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023007_e00030",
      "play_id": "01023007",
      "scene_id": "01023007_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘福通"
      ],
      "text": "备得酒宴，要与御弟痛饮。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023007_e00031",
      "play_id": "01023007",
      "scene_id": "01023007_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "朱元璋"
      ],
      "text": "到此就要叨扰。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023007_e00032",
      "play_id": "01023007",
      "scene_id": "01023007_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘福通"
      ],
      "text": "看宴。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023007_e00033",
      "play_id": "01023007",
      "scene_id": "01023007_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "〖吹打〗。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023007_e00034",
      "play_id": "01023007",
      "scene_id": "01023007_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘福通"
      ],
      "text": "请。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023007_e00035",
      "play_id": "01023007",
      "scene_id": "01023007_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "朱元璋"
      ],
      "text": "请。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023007_e00036",
      "play_id": "01023007",
      "scene_id": "01023007_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘福通"
      ],
      "text": "来，舞剑上来！",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023007_e00037",
      "play_id": "01023007",
      "scene_id": "01023007_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "吴通耍剑，刺朱元璋，吴桢踢吴通。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023007_e00038",
      "play_id": "01023007",
      "scene_id": "01023007_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "吴桢"
      ],
      "text": "大胆！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023007_e00039",
      "play_id": "01023007",
      "scene_id": "01023007_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "吴桢"
      ],
      "text": "小番儿行事太狂妄，擅敢在酒宴前刺杀君王。事到如今无有话讲，杀了那刘福通再做商量。",
      "text_length": 40
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023007_e00040",
      "play_id": "01023007",
      "scene_id": "01023007_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "吴桢砍刘福通，众人同拦，吴桢拉朱元璋同下，众人同追下。",
      "text_length": 27
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023007_e00041",
      "play_id": "01023007",
      "scene_id": "01023007_s06",
      "scene_no": 6,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "放火。朱元璋上，烧，跑下。众人同上，跑圆场，同下。",
      "text_length": 25
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023007_e00042",
      "play_id": "01023007",
      "scene_id": "01023007_s07",
      "scene_no": 7,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "蒋忠上，看两边。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023007_e00043",
      "play_id": "01023007",
      "scene_id": "01023007_s07",
      "scene_no": 7,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "蒋忠"
      ],
      "text": "站立在坡前用目望，又只见楼上放火光。倘若是有人将吾主来挡，今日里我定要血战沙场。",
      "text_length": 40
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023007_e00044",
      "play_id": "01023007",
      "scene_id": "01023007_s07",
      "scene_no": 7,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "蒋忠下。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023007_e00045",
      "play_id": "01023007",
      "scene_id": "01023007_s08",
      "scene_no": 8,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "朱元璋上，烧。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023007_e00046",
      "play_id": "01023007",
      "scene_id": "01023007_s08",
      "scene_no": 8,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "朱元璋"
      ],
      "text": "恼恨那刘福通贼奸党，为何故放火焚烧百凉？四下里火焰起无处逃往，怕的是君臣们难回朝堂。",
      "text_length": 42
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023007_e00047",
      "play_id": "01023007",
      "scene_id": "01023007_s08",
      "scene_no": 8,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "朱元璋倒。吴桢上，看两边，扶朱元璋起。",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023007_e00048",
      "play_id": "01023007",
      "scene_id": "01023007_s08",
      "scene_no": 8,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄导板",
      "speakers": [
        "朱元璋"
      ],
      "text": "一霎时烧得孤三魂飘荡，",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023007_e00049",
      "play_id": "01023007",
      "scene_id": "01023007_s08",
      "scene_no": 8,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "朱元璋"
      ],
      "text": "又只见老将军站立一旁。我君臣今入了天罗地网，",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023007_e00050",
      "play_id": "01023007",
      "scene_id": "01023007_s08",
      "scene_no": 8,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "吴桢"
      ],
      "text": "那贼兵好一似铁壁铜墙。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023007_e00051",
      "play_id": "01023007",
      "scene_id": "01023007_s08",
      "scene_no": 8,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "朱元璋"
      ],
      "text": "老将军你一人怎能抵挡？",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023007_e00052",
      "play_id": "01023007",
      "scene_id": "01023007_s08",
      "scene_no": 8,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "吴桢"
      ],
      "text": "但愿得大兵到转回朝堂。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023007_e00053",
      "play_id": "01023007",
      "scene_id": "01023007_s08",
      "scene_no": 8,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "蒋忠上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023007_e00054",
      "play_id": "01023007",
      "scene_id": "01023007_s08",
      "scene_no": 8,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "蒋忠"
      ],
      "text": "牵战马来至在乱石岗上，只见那老吴桢扶保吾王。走向前请我主快把马上，",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023007_e00055",
      "play_id": "01023007",
      "scene_id": "01023007_s08",
      "scene_no": 8,
      "seq_global": 55,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "朱元璋上马，急下。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023007_e00056",
      "play_id": "01023007",
      "scene_id": "01023007_s08",
      "scene_no": 8,
      "seq_global": 56,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "蒋忠"
      ],
      "text": "老将军与某家同赴战场。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023007_e00057",
      "play_id": "01023007",
      "scene_id": "01023007_s08",
      "scene_no": 8,
      "seq_global": 57,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "吴桢"
      ],
      "text": "我这里提枪把马上，",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023007_e00058",
      "play_id": "01023007",
      "scene_id": "01023007_s08",
      "scene_no": 8,
      "seq_global": 58,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "吴桢夺旗内枪，上马。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023007_e00059",
      "play_id": "01023007",
      "scene_id": "01023007_s08",
      "scene_no": 8,
      "seq_global": 59,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "吴桢"
      ],
      "text": "要与番贼动刀枪。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023007_e00060",
      "play_id": "01023007",
      "scene_id": "01023007_s08",
      "scene_no": 8,
      "seq_global": 60,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "吴桢、蒋忠同下。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023007_e00061",
      "play_id": "01023007",
      "scene_id": "01023007_s09",
      "scene_no": 9,
      "seq_global": 61,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "四上手、沐英同上。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023007_e00062",
      "play_id": "01023007",
      "scene_id": "01023007_s09",
      "scene_no": 9,
      "seq_global": 62,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "沐英"
      ],
      "text": "俺，沐英。哪里有喊杀之声，登高一望。",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023007_e00063",
      "play_id": "01023007",
      "scene_id": "01023007_s09",
      "scene_no": 9,
      "seq_global": 63,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "沐英上山。吴桢上，刘福通追上，开打，吴桢败下。蒋忠上，开打，众人同败下，蒋忠追下。",
      "text_length": 41
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023007_e00064",
      "play_id": "01023007",
      "scene_id": "01023007_s09",
      "scene_no": 9,
      "seq_global": 64,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "沐英"
      ],
      "text": "乃是番兵与吾主交战，待我向前帮助便了。",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023007_e00065",
      "play_id": "01023007",
      "scene_id": "01023007_s09",
      "scene_no": 9,
      "seq_global": 65,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "四上手、沐英同下。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023007_e00066",
      "play_id": "01023007",
      "scene_id": "01023007_s10",
      "scene_no": 10,
      "seq_global": 66,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "四龙套、刘福通同上。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023007_e00067",
      "play_id": "01023007",
      "scene_id": "01023007_s10",
      "scene_no": 10,
      "seq_global": 67,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘福通"
      ],
      "text": "看那厮杀法厉害，来，弓箭手伺候！（蒋忠上，四龙套同追上，同开打。刘福通败下，四龙套同追下。四弓箭手同上，埋伏。刘福通上，蒋忠追上。四弓箭手同放箭，沐英上，救蒋忠同下。众人同下。）",
      "text_length": 89
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023007_e00068",
      "play_id": "01023007",
      "scene_id": "01023007_s11",
      "scene_no": 11,
      "seq_global": 68,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "吴桢、朱元璋同上，沐英背蒋忠同上。蒋忠哭。",
      "text_length": 21
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023007_e00069",
      "play_id": "01023007",
      "scene_id": "01023007_s11",
      "scene_no": 11,
      "seq_global": 69,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "朱元璋"
      ],
      "text": "你是何人前来帮助？",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023007_e00070",
      "play_id": "01023007",
      "scene_id": "01023007_s11",
      "scene_no": 11,
      "seq_global": 70,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "沐英"
      ],
      "text": "臣沐英，救驾来迟，万岁恕罪！",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023007_e00071",
      "play_id": "01023007",
      "scene_id": "01023007_s11",
      "scene_no": 11,
      "seq_global": 71,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "朱元璋"
      ],
      "text": "你敢么就是钱塘大汉沐英么？",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023007_e00072",
      "play_id": "01023007",
      "scene_id": "01023007_s11",
      "scene_no": 11,
      "seq_global": 72,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "沐英"
      ],
      "text": "正是。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023007_e00073",
      "play_id": "01023007",
      "scene_id": "01023007_s11",
      "scene_no": 11,
      "seq_global": 73,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "朱元璋"
      ],
      "text": "久已闻名，今日相逢，孤之幸也。保孤回朝，定有封赠。",
      "text_length": 25
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023007_e00074",
      "play_id": "01023007",
      "scene_id": "01023007_s11",
      "scene_no": 11,
      "seq_global": 74,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "沐英"
      ],
      "text": "谢万岁！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023007_e00075",
      "play_id": "01023007",
      "scene_id": "01023007_s11",
      "scene_no": 11,
      "seq_global": 75,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "四龙套引刘福通同上，朱元璋下。开打，吴桢、沐英同败下，众人同追下。",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023007_e00076",
      "play_id": "01023007",
      "scene_id": "01023007_s12",
      "scene_no": 12,
      "seq_global": 76,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "〖急急风〗。四龙套、八将、常遇春同上。",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023007_e00077",
      "play_id": "01023007",
      "scene_id": "01023007_s12",
      "scene_no": 12,
      "seq_global": 77,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "常遇春"
      ],
      "text": "俺，常遇春。我主去赴兴隆大会，恐有不测，不免前去保驾便了。众将官，杀上前去！",
      "text_length": 38
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023007_e00078",
      "play_id": "01023007",
      "scene_id": "01023007_s12",
      "scene_no": 12,
      "seq_global": 78,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "四龙套、刘福通同上，对阵，起打。八股荡连环，刘福通、四龙套同败下，常遇春、八将、四龙套同追下。",
      "text_length": 47
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023007_e00079",
      "play_id": "01023007",
      "scene_id": "01023007_s13",
      "scene_no": 13,
      "seq_global": 79,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "四龙套、刘福通同上，同入城，关门。常遇春、八将、四龙套同追上。城内摇旗。常遇春三笑，同下。",
      "text_length": 45
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023007_e00080",
      "play_id": "01023007",
      "scene_id": "01023007_s14",
      "scene_no": 14,
      "seq_global": 80,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "朱元璋、吴桢、沐英同上。四龙套、八将、常遇春同上。",
      "text_length": 25
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023007_e00081",
      "play_id": "01023007",
      "scene_id": "01023007_s14",
      "scene_no": 14,
      "seq_global": 81,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "常遇春"
      ],
      "text": "臣，常遇春救驾来迟，吾主恕罪。",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023007_e00082",
      "play_id": "01023007",
      "scene_id": "01023007_s14",
      "scene_no": 14,
      "seq_global": 82,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "朱元璋"
      ],
      "text": "卿之功也。一同回朝。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023007_e00083",
      "play_id": "01023007",
      "scene_id": "01023007_s14",
      "scene_no": 14,
      "seq_global": 83,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "〖吹打〗。众人同下。",
      "text_length": 10
    }
